1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper proposes a proactive network protection scheme and discusses its implementation and performance in networks. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper involves encoding and decoding of data streams, which is a key concept in information theory. 
3. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) - The paper discusses the implementation of the algorithm in networks, which involves distributed computing and parallel processing. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a system for network protection and discusses its performance in terms of link failure recovery. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper discusses network protection, which is a key aspect of network security.
